I have a product card with a name, price, and rating stars. How should I label it for VoiceOver?

```swift
VStack {
    Text(product.name)
    Text("$\(product.price)")
    HStack {
        ForEach(0..<5) { i in
            Image(systemName: i < product.rating ? "star.fill" : "star")
        }
    }
}
```
